T02D3635:250b-1: ma h'a ba la s'a dha nam /
T02D3635:250b-4: khro bo'i rgyal po stobs po che la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3635:250b-5: sngon dug sungs pa'i cho gas stong pa nyid kyis
T02D3635:250b-6: mthar padma dkar po dang nyi ma la h'um yig
T02D3635:250b-7: las byung ba'i stobs bo che zhal gcig pa phyag
T02D3635:250b-8: bzhi pa sku mdog thams cad dmar po //
T02D3635:250b-9: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du 'khyil pa /
T02D3635:250b-11: phag g-yas pa gnyis kyis dbyug pa dkar po dang /
T02D3635:250b-13: phyag g-yon pa gnyis kyis phyag 'tshal ba'i tshul dang /
T02D3635:250b-14: zhags pa dang bcas pa'i sdigs mdzub mdzad pa /
T02D3635:250b-15: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can /
T02D3635:250b-18: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'od kyi phreng ba can /
T02D3635:250b-19: 'od dpag tu med pas dbu brgyan pa bsgom par bya'o //
T02D3635:250b-21: aom ma h'a ba la sv'a h'a /
